                    <title>OperationsInc acquires AllCountyJobs.com Job Board Network</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://jobboarders.com/xn/detail/882452:BlogPost:89699"/>
                                        <id>tag:jobboarders.com,2012-05-31:882452:BlogPost:89699</id>
                                        <updated>2012-05-31T17:30:00.000Z</updated>
                    
                                            <author>
                            <name>Chris Russell</name>
                            <uri>http://jobboarders.com/profile/job_board_consultant</uri>
                        </author>
                    
                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;29 Sites included in purchase covering all of CT, as well as other local regions &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Stamford, CT. [May 31, 2012] It is with great pleasure that &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.operationsinc.com/&quot;&gt;OperationsInc&lt;/a&gt;,  announces the acquisition of leading local job board, AllCountyJobs.com (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.allcountyjobs.com/&quot;&gt;www.AllCountyJobs.com&lt;/a&gt;). The purchase includes a total of 29 Job Boards covering the Northeast US Corridor.&lt;span class=&quot;s3&quot;&gt; The decision to…&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;29 Sites included in purchase covering all of CT, as well as other local regions &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Stamford, CT. [May 31, 2012] It is with great pleasure that &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.operationsinc.com/&quot;&gt;OperationsInc&lt;/a&gt;,  announces the acquisition of leading local job board, AllCountyJobs.com (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.allcountyjobs.com/&quot;&gt;www.AllCountyJobs.com&lt;/a&gt;). The purchase includes a total of 29 Job Boards covering the Northeast US Corridor.&lt;span class=&quot;s3&quot;&gt; The decision to make this acquisition was tied to multiple factors, including the opportunity to exploit countless synergies between the two firms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;OperationsInc’s  plans include growing the content and popularity of each site by offering enhanced services to both the employer and candidate populations, leveraging their expertise as one of the nation’s top subject matter experts in the world of Human Resources, as well as in the recruiting field.&lt;span class=&quot;s5&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s3&quot;&gt;Terms of the deal are confidential and will not be disclosed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s4&quot;&gt;“I’d like to personally thank the thousands of employers and job seekers who have used my job boards over the past 13 years, said Chris Russell, who founded AllCountyJobs in 1999. “It has been a pleasure to work with you. The success of the sites has been a fantastic journey for me. Now I get to watch OperationsInc build upon that success and take them to the next level.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p6&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s6&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s4&quot;&gt;Acquiring AllCountyJobs.com is one of the most exciting milestones for our firm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s6&quot;&gt;” stated David Lewis, President of OperationsInc.“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s4&quot;&gt; It represents an opportunity to build on the success Chris has created in the array of sites while also leveraging our knowledge and expertise in the areas of job seeking for both employers and candidates. We are looking forward to years of success as the two firms leverage one another’s strengths and capabilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s6&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Founded by David Lewis in 2001, OperationsInc specializes in HR solutions for small businesses and HR professionals. OperationsInc’s portfolio of offerings includes such services as: Human Resources Outsourcing, Recruitment and Retention Services, Outplacement Services, Benefits Administration, Exit Interview Services, Payroll Administration and Management and Staff Training. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p7&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;OperationsInc is located at 992 High Ridge Road, Second Floor, Stamford, CT 06905 and David can be reached at (203) 322-0538 or &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@operationsinc.com&quot;&gt;info@operationsinc.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Chris Russell can be reached at (&lt;span class=&quot;s3&quot;&gt;203) 572-2053 &lt;/span&gt;or &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:chris@allcountyjobs.com&quot;&gt;chris@allcountyjobs.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;stat-clear&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
