&lt;p&gt;The 2011 IAEWS Benchmarking Survey was a huge success, but don’t take my word for it.  Visit the IAEWS home page (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.EmploymentWebSites.org&quot;&gt;www.EmploymentWebSites.org&lt;/a&gt;) and take a look at the video that’s posted there.  You’ll hear from the survey co-chair, Matt Hoffner of Jobg8.com, and from two IAEWS Members who participated in both the survey and the discussion forum on its results.  Steven Rothberg of CollegeRecruiter.com and Andy Hibel of HigherEdJobs.com provide some firsthand insight on both the experience and value of their participation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
