&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#555555&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#222222&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://api.ning.com:80/files/ajl0Ao2j4GXRac7W2Ub8PB3RHTjxPiZZGrW3bivuf6sE6JKtI8J5kfkDLN0xu0cDWJy2k2fTDGVoDgDDgIDEww__/JobDescriptionOnResume.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://api.ning.com:80/files/ajl0Ao2j4GXRac7W2Ub8PB3RHTjxPiZZGrW3bivuf6sE6JKtI8J5kfkDLN0xu0cDWJy2k2fTDGVoDgDDgIDEww__/JobDescriptionOnResume.jpg&quot; width=&quot;246&quot; class=&quot;align-right&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#555555&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#222222&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are experience candidate then for you &lt;strong&gt;describing your work experience&lt;/strong&gt; on resume is a good point. But describe your work in &lt;strong&gt;professional&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;career oriented manner&lt;/strong&gt;. Explain your job profile along with responsibilities, company name, and your designation. Also include any achievements in job description which may be key point. Mention all the information of current plus previous job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#555555&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#222222&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Verdana, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
